# Medium

It is the api for Medium Blog

# Group login Authentication

This group contain resources  related to login authentication

## SignUp page  [/signup]

This is for the new user

### Sign Up [POST]

you may create your own account

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "username": "userid",
            "password":"password" 
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
           {
             "id":"unique id of user"
             "userid":"xyz@gmail.com"
             "article":["article_id","article_id"]
             "bookmarks":["userid+article_id","userid+article_id"]
           
           }
        ]
        
+ Response 301 (application/json)

        [
            {
               "error":"authentication failed"
            }
        ]
        
