# Group article Manipulation

This group contain resources  related to artice manipulation

## article request  [/article]

Here you can requst for the article based on  article id

### article [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "article": "articleid"
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
           {
             "id":"articleid"
             "userid":"xyz@gmail.com"
              "type":[]
              "title":"title of article"
              "description":"description about article"
               "likes":"0"
           }
        ]